column5:
↜Warrior↝
戦士

Hello from the Ethernal. We are working with artist Komiyama Takashi again on a pixel art collection: Ethernal x Hermippe Heroes. This is the fourth in the collection, for those who never misses a battle. The Warrior wields his sword everyday.

Based on the Ethernal hero classes, we are releasing a total of 5 artworks: a new limited artwork every 14 days. Each artwork will have a maximum of 20 art tokens.

Each token comes with: High-resolution JPEG and animated GIF files + Original sketch + Mobile wallpapers. Collect all five tokens to receive special high-resolution JPEG and animated GIF files with all the heroes in portrait and landscape views.

After you purchase the art token, email enter@ethernal.world with the address that owns the token to receive the bundle.

Hello from the Ethernal. This is the first of our limited edition art series. For our upcoming Alpha 2.0 release, we have worked with artist Komiyama Takashi on a pixel art token 「the entrance」. “There’s a reason they have stayed away, but the reason you’ve come is stronger still.” 

This token comes with: High resolution .jpeg and animated .gif files in portrait and landscape views + Original sketch + Desktop & mobile wallpapers

After you purchase the art token, email enter@ethernal.world with the address that owns the token to receive the bundle. 

Limited to 20.

ΔYa-shaΔ
夜叉

Hello from the Ethernal. We are working with artist Komiyama Takashi again on a pixel art collection: Ethernal x Hermippe Heroes. This is the fifth (and last) in the collection. A Ya-sha ninja lurks in the dark, waiting for a definitive attack.

Based on the Ethernal hero classes, we are releasing a total of 5 artworks: a new limited artwork every 14 days. Each artwork will have a maximum of 20 art tokens.

Each token comes with: High-resolution JPEG and animated GIF files + Original sketch + Mobile wallpapers. Collect all five tokens to receive special high-resolution JPEG and animated GIF files with all the heroes in portrait and landscape views.

After you purchase the art token, email enter@ethernal.world with the address that owns the token to receive the bundle.
